### Install and load packages

This workshop will use the packages `tidyverse` (for data manipulation and plotting), `gtsummary` (for table formatting) and `medicaldata` for example datasets.

```{r eval=T, echo=T, message = F, warning = F}
library(tidyverse)
library(gtsummary)
library(medicaldata)
```


### Example data used

This session will use the `smartpill` dataset included in the `medicaldata` package.

Load the [`trial` dataset](https://www.danieldsjoberg.com/gtsummary/reference/trial.html?q=trial#ref-usage) and [`cytomegalovirus` data](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/medicaldata/refman/medicaldata.html#cytomegalovirus)


```{r eval=T, echo=T}
attach(cytomegalovirus)
data(cytomegalovirus)
```

